data.description: Welcome to this Charming one-story home nested in a quiet neighborhood of Katy zoned to distinguished Katy ISD schools. This adorable home is filled with plenty of natural lights and features an open floor plan perfect for entertaining. The Gourmet Kitchen is equipped with plenty of cabinets for storage and generous countertop spaces. Refrigerator and Washer/dryer are negotiable. The spacious Primary master suite has an updated en-suite primary bath. The two secondary bedrooms with spacious closets are located on the opposite side with a full bath. Enjoy the huge breathtaking backyard with a covered patio. Easy access to I-10, Grand Pkwy, and major shopping centers makes this house the perfect home. Schedule your showing before this beauty is gone!
